## 6️⃣ Accessibility in React (Very Important)

### ✅ HTML‑first approach

```jsx
<button onClick={save}>Save</button>
```

✅ No ARIA needed

***

### ✅ When ARIA is required

```jsx
<div
  role="button"
  tabIndex={0}
  aria-label="Close"
  onClick={close}
/>
```

***

## 7️⃣ Keyboard Accessibility Attributes

### ✅ `tabIndex`



*   `0` → keyboard focusable
*   `-1` → programmatically focusable

***

